@node 8 Templates
Four templates: Guide & text if you want to write some docs. MUI for MUI apps and Type for the new filetypes icons. These icons are a little bit reduced in size if you compare them with BNS's ones.
I reduced the template so that left-out files get an icon which has the same height that appicons (tool template).
@endnode

